summary: I know you didn't ask this, but about what you said in the tags about dan making a therapy video, i would like to tell you that...
question: I know you didn't ask this, but about what you said in the tags about dan making a therapy video, i would like to tell you that there's nothing to worry about. I've been going to therapy since i was 5, I went to a psychologist when i was younger and right now i go to a psychologist and to a psychiatrist (one for therapy the other for meds) and honestly it improves so much in my life! It's just a matter of finding a professional you can trust, and it will really help with a lot! 10/10 recommend
answer: aww thanks for responding about that! I’ve been to a few therapists before in the last year but I really didn’t like them and it’s just super hard for me to talk to a random stranger but I really need help so I’ll try to make another appointment soon. thanks for your input!!
